              Empowering car owners to fight for fair insurance payouts using the industry-standard 17c Formula and data-driven calculations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Resources -->
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Resources</h3>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem;">
              <li><a href="https://www.kbb.com" target="_blank" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">Kelley Blue Book</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.nada.com" target="_blank" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">NADA Guides</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">17c Formula Guide</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">FAQ</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Legal -->
          <div>
            <h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Legal</h3>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.625rem;">
              <li><a href="#" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">Privacy Policy</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s;">Terms of Service</a></li>
